lead_paragraph: Guards Kyle Lowry and DeMar DeRozan combined for 59 points as the Toronto Raptors beat the Portland Trail Blazers 110-103 at the Moda Center on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Lowry, DeRozan Lead Raptors Past Trail Blazers
